{"tid":653454,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"UEFA擺烏龍 利記未踢決賽攞冠軍","createTime":"2018-05-04T17:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T19:26:45.000Z","uid":20634,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3993e15fa32ebf7e299eeb76de95e74fd7d4b00c","tid":653454,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/0/600/21316866600/21316373313_523x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F0%2F600%2F21316866600%2F21316373313_523x420.jpg&h=94175707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=LiGpq4PHcy29c2DU02GkF%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=50e25dce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦贏得今季歐聯！這當然不是未卜先知，而是歐洲足協官方網的失誤。<br />\n<br />\nUEFA在周五令人意外地，在官方網站其中一個版面展示一張圖片，圖中列明利物浦是2017/18年球季的冠軍隊。這個錯處雖然很快獲得修正，但在互聯網的世界自然是幾何式的發送，這錯版立時被cap圖並已在網上流傳。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦在周中苦戰下，兩回合計以7:6淘汰羅馬，將於5月26日在基輔與皇家馬德里爭奪賽事冠軍。後者晉級過程亦非輕鬆，於周中與拜仁慕尼黑各二言和後，勝4:3晉級。<br />\n<br />\n這將是兩軍歷來第6次在歐聯或歐冠盃對陣，紅軍對賽往績稍佳，之前5次對陣，紅軍取得3勝2負，而皇馬對上一次在歐聯決賽輸波是1981年，正是以0:1不敵利物浦。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 互聯網"},{"pid":"beed201173a070a34517811cbe2f794a957e7a83","tid":653454,"uid":85461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:38:05.000Z","msg":"黑撚到佢"},{"pid":"b1a499ed4aa13d87923a33644700e7d50622f919","tid":653454,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:29:14.000Z","msg":"喂咪踢爆啦"},{"pid":"ade7beebe914838c8aac02840ffdd85cbc8e218e","tid":653454,"uid":22506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c036b95f574b6c327f532f041b1207724d0fe58","tid":653454,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0